data.description: Welcome to this charming residence nestled in the desirable Gahanna Jefferson Schools district! Step inside to discover a delightful interior with refinished hardwood floors that flow from the inviting living room to the adjacent dining area. Entertain effortlessly as you access the deck from the dining room, offering a wonderful view of the fenced backyard.The gourmet kitchen features modern countertops, sleek cabinets, and an elegant white subway tile backsplash. Upstairs, retreat to three generously sized bedrooms and a renovated full bathroom. The lower level has been thoughtfully finished to include a half bath, cozy family room with a convenient access to the backyard, and a functional utility area. Improvements also include the furnace, AC and hot water tank that are 5 years young.
